info.title: They Do Not Die (Reskin)
info.author: ThatOtherPerson
info.details:
They Do Not Die is a zombie shooter.

Now with enhanced graphics and an all new custom
map, Zombie Death Maze! -- Navigate the maze 
and make it to the Safe House at the end! 
(Extras by Mr. Reaper)	
	
Controls:
Nunchuck analog stick = Move
A button = Run
B button = Shoot

Author:
